        <updateDate>2007-07-02T19:03:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>End Discriminatory State Taxes for Automobile Renters Act of 2007 - Prohibits states or local governments from levying or collecting a discriminatory tax (as defined by this Act) on the rental of motor vehicles, motor vehicle rental businesses, or motor vehicle rental property. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
